data.description: The meticulously renovated two-story home boasts four bedrooms, three and a half baths, and a three-car garage, all tucked away on a peaceful cul-de-sac with a basketball hoop. The property features a stunningly updated kitchen with brand new stainless steel appliances, elegantly remodeled bathrooms, freshly installed windows, interior doors, trim, lighting fixtures, and hardware. The entire interior and exterior have been expertly repainted.The finished basement includes a third full bathroom, an additional bedroom, an office space, and a versatile family/playroom. In addition to the three-car garage, the house sits on a generously wide lot, offering ample space for outdoor activities and expansion. This home is impeccably prepared and eagerly awaits its new owner
